data.description: Motivated Seller . Rarely available, perfect home, clean and upgraded, Windsor Bay, Coral Springs, gated community, triple split home. There are 4 bedrooms, plus den-office with a door which is a 5th bedroom, separate living room and dining room and a separate family room.  Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, neutral tile floors in living areas. Updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Spacious bedrooms with split floor plan, master bedroom with tray ceilings & a walk-in closet. Master Bathroom with dual sinks, roman tub & separate shower. Very low HOA . Great private backyard to entertain for many occasions. A must see.
